{
  "stem": "2735.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "He was going-- he was going to beg by the-- like a little out of town and beg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And one time they found him frozen to death, sitting there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And the villagers wouldn't bury him because the ground was so hard that they used to keep them till they had about 10 and then dig a hole.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "It was-- at 12 o'clock it used to get dark, at four o'clock, it was pitch-- I mean, even after 12 o'clock, because there was-- everything was closed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "There was no mail, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the postmaster of the village approached me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says if I could give lessons to her daughter, she said she'll try to help us with the food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went through like fields, and I heard wolves howling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And each time-- yeah, so my-- the old woman that I lived was so impressed that I'm a teacher, I work in the office, she gave me a woolen boots to wear.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So each time I put it in, I had to work real hard to pull this one out and the other one fell in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, it didn't work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went there a few times and I couldn't-- I mean, I couldn't get there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she couldn't get out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we lived there for nine months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we couldn't wait till it will start-- the snow would start thawing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In May it started to thaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now while I was there in the office, at one time there's this boy came-- I mean he was harassing me all the time, sexually, stalking me out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was 19.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was almost-- I was 20 already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- he came to call me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says somebody wants to see you.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
